#: index.html%2Bsection.div.div.div.div.div.p:67-13
msgid ""
"Ceno is based on <a href=\"https://mozac.org/\">Mozilla Android Components</"
"a>, extended to make use of the <a href=\"https://gitlab.com/equalitie/"
"ouinet\">Ouinet library</a> - enabling third party developers to incorporate "
"the Ceno network into their apps for P2P connectivity."
msgstr ""
